TopicTitle: KSP won't launch after clean reinstall (MacOS)

Articles.Content:
I just got KSP a couple days ago and I've been getting mods and progressing and what not. I downloaded some mods from CKAN and they all worked perfectly, just recently when I tried to download some Near Future mods, the joint reinforcement mod and a couple others(can't remember). Tried to start KSP again and it would crash at "Module Manager: Running post patch callbacks".

I deleted the mods I downloaded and still same problem when I tried to open up KSP. I saved my GameData folder and my user saves, did a clean reinstall, but now it crashes right when I open it up and it gives me this crash report attached below. 

Hope someone can help me, really trying to play KSP again
